wiki.content: "Feather" is a song by American singer Sabrina Carpenter from Emails I Can’t Send Fwd:, the deluxe edition of her fifth studio album released in 2022. Carpenter and Amy Allen wrote the song with its producer, John Ryan. "Feather" is a pop song about overcoming a relationship. Incorporating electric piano, piano, synthesizer, kick, and bass in its instrumentation, the song's lyrics detail blocking someone on social media and feeling like a burden has been lifted after leaving them behind: "I got you blocked / After this, an afterthought / I finally cut you off / I feel so much lighter, like a feather with you off my mind." Island Records released its sped-up version for digital download and streaming on August 4, 2023. A music video for the song was released on October 31, 2023. Read more on Last.fm.
